item.title: How do you obtain RuneScape #377 Song ID's?
item.dc:creator: @Level_120_Dungeoneer Level 120 Dungeoneering
item.description:
@Level_120_Dungeoneer wrote:

[quote=“zyle1992, post:2, topic:441245”]From what I remember, the sounds weren’t actually stored in the cache (well, not all of them at least). If I recall, the sounds were sent by the server on demand, cached for the lifetime of the session, and then discarded when the client was closed.

I can be wrong though, I haven’t experimented much with the sounds. (also, packet 74 seems to contradict my memory)[/quote]
No, you’re thinking of how the #317 cache played music. The #377 cache had ID’s.
